Wazuh Installation steps
 
Step 1
Make sure the server has minimum requirments met for wazuh installation (Ram-4gb, CPU cores-2)

curl -sO https://packages.wazuh.com/4.7/wazuh-install.sh
curl -sO https://packages.wazuh.com/4.7/config.yml

(vist wazuh official documentation https://documentation.wazuh.com/current/installation-guide/wazuh-indexer/installation-assistant.html
for updated links)
 
Step 2 
Edit the config.yml file (add your server ip address and desired name in the ip and name sections)
 
Step 3
 
bash wazuh-install.sh -a 
Run this command and wazuh will start the whole process
 
End.
